dc_title_s: Map showing the survey of lands under the waters of the Hudson River and Bay of New York and of lands adjacent thereto
dc_description_s: Riparian map of the Hudson River, featuring the waterfront road and railway system from Hoboken in Hudson County to Harrinton Township, Bergen County|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Traced by S.B. Scales|Map is a tracing, made in 1920 of an original created in 1865
